2024-12-02 16:26:10 - StudioAtrium\Entity\Discuss\Post:Insert {"timestamp":1733156770,"user_id":null,"user_ip":"89.8.37.9","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (iPhone; CPU iPhone OS 17_5_1 like Mac OS X) AppleWebKit\/605.1.15 (KHTML, like Gecko) CriOS\/131.0.6778.73 Mobile\/15E148 Safari\/604.1","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_insert","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post","entity_data":{"id":10323,"__foreign_props":[],"parent_id":"0","cat_id":"100","project_id":"1314","nick":"Mariola","topic":"Usuni\u0119cie gara\u017cu","content":"Witam, czy mo\u017cna usun\u0105\u0107 z projektu gara\u017c i doda\u0107 dodatkowy pok\u00f3j? Przenie\u015b\u0107 ma\u0142\u0105 \u0142azienk\u0119 na \u015bcian\u0119 z komjnmkiem? Dodatkowo doda\u0107 pralni\u0119, zmieni\u0107 k\u0105t nachylenia dachu i powi\u0119kszy\u0107 salon o po\u0142ow\u0119 tarasu? Na ile pozwalacie na takie zmiany ?","create_date":"2024-12-02 16:26:10","modify_date":"2024-12-02 16:26:10","status":"published","is_moderated":0,"attachments":[],"_uid":2642735},"entity_changes":false}
