2024-12-02 16:27:59 - StudioAtrium\Entity\User:Update {"timestamp":1733156879,"user_id":17547,"user_ip":"37.31.53.129","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64; rv:133.0) Gecko\/20100101 Firefox\/133.0","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\User\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_update","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\User","entity_data":{"id":17547,"__foreign_props":[],"type":"user","email":"pawelpiti@hotmail.com","password":"ac810799c4ab6337a467d9d4e0ec72a91824978acf7f056c34daabb08471ca57","name":"Pawe\u0142","surname":"Pituch","nick":"","status":"enabled","register_date":"2024-12-01 13:38:08","props":{"favourite":["1288","1240"]},"attachments":[],"_uid":4492033,"impersonated":false},"entity_changes":{"props":"{\"favourite\":[\"1288\",\"1240\"]}"}}
2024-12-02 16:43:05 - StudioAtrium\Entity\User\Message:Update {"timestamp":1733157785,"user_id":17462,"user_ip":"89.8.37.196","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (iPhone; CPU iPhone OS 17_5_1 like Mac OS X) AppleWebKit\/605.1.15 (KHTML, like Gecko) CriOS\/131.0.6778.73 Mobile\/15E148 Safari\/604.1","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\User\\Message\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_update","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\User\\Message","entity_data":{"id":1289,"__foreign_props":[],"user_id":"17462","parent_id":"1287","author":"Studio Atrium","title":"Re: Projekt Pliszka v","message":"<p>Tak. Tak\u0105 zmian\u0119 na 35 stopni mo\u017cemy wykona\u0107 w naszej pracowni za dodatkow\u0105 op\u0142at\u0105 1000z\u0142, b\u0105d\u017a zleci\u0107 j\u0105 podobnie jak wcze\u015bniej opisane zmiany lokalnemu projektantowi. Wtedy wszelkie kwestie zwi\u0105zane z takimi zmianami nale\u017ca\u0142o b\u0119dzie ustala\u0107 ju\u017c z nim bezpo\u015brednio.<\/p>\r\n<p>Je\u017celi b\u0119dzie Pani zainteresowana zakupem projektu, czy to w wariancie ze zmian\u0105 k\u0105ta nachylenia dachu, czy bez takowej, pozostaj\u0119 do dyspozycji.<\/p>\r\n<p>Pozdrawiam<br \/>\u0141ukasz Jakubiec<\/p>","create_date":"2024-11-08 14:14:47","status":"read","attachments":[],"_uid":330020},"entity_changes":{"status":"read"}}
2024-12-02 16:43:05 - StudioAtrium\Entity\User\Message:Update {"timestamp":1733157785,"user_id":17462,"user_ip":"89.8.37.196","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (iPhone; CPU iPhone OS 17_5_1 like Mac OS X) AppleWebKit\/605.1.15 (KHTML, like Gecko) CriOS\/131.0.6778.73 Mobile\/15E148 Safari\/604.1","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\User\\Message\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_update","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\User\\Message","entity_data":{"id":1288,"__foreign_props":[],"user_id":"17462","parent_id":"1286","author":"Studio Atrium","title":"Re: Zapytanie o projekt Pliszka V","message":"<p>Dzie\u0144 dobry<\/p>\r\n<p>Jak najbardziej istnieje mo\u017cliwo\u015b\u0107 prowadzenia takich zmian w projekcie. S\u0105 one jednak na tyle indywidualne, \u017ce nale\u017ca\u0142o je b\u0119dzie zleci\u0107 lokalnemu projektantowi, kt\u00f3ry b\u0119dzie dla Pani wykonywa\u0142 adaptacj\u0119 projektu do warunk\u00f3w miejscowych. Z naszej strony wydamy Pani bezp\u0142atn\u0105 zgod\u0119 na tego typu zmiany.<br \/>W przypadku dodatkowych pyta\u0144, pozostaj\u0119 w kontakcie.<\/p>\r\n<p>Pozdrawiam<br \/>\u0141ukasz Jakubiec<\/p>","create_date":"2024-11-08 14:12:13","status":"read","attachments":[],"_uid":329764},"entity_changes":{"status":"read"}}
